General information






About Makpetrol AD



	Makpetrol AD is a Macedonian company, specialised in the wholesale and retail of petroleum products.

	The company is included in the MBI10 blue-chip index of the Macedonian Stock Exchange (MSE).

	Makpetrol AD holds an ISO 27001:2013 Information security management systems certificate, valid until July 9, 2017.

Last updated on July 22, 2016.



