Products and services




	Makpetrol AD is engaged in:

	1. Management of filling stations;

	2. Retail sale of food and non-food items;

	3. Wholesale of:


		Liquefied petroleum gas (LPG);

		Biodiesel;

		Heating oil;

		Jet fuel;

		Natural gas;

		Fuel oil;

		Bitumen;

		Glycerine;

		Oils and lubricants


	4. Freight forwarding;
	5. Hotel management.







